<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="sleep-n">sleep <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /sliːp/    美 /sliːp/  </p>
<p>[U] &amp; [C]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>睡；睡眠：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a <strong>light / deep sleep</strong>
浅/深睡眠</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He <strong>went to sleep</strong> while he was in church. 
他在教堂里做礼拜时睡着了。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I couldn’t <strong>get to sleep</strong> last night. 
我昨晚睡不着。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">派生词汇</h2>
<p>sleepless /'sliːpləs/ adj   </p></div>